com.gwtplatform.mvp.rebind

Interface ProxyOutputter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicProxyOutputter, NonLeafTabContentProxyOutputter, ProxyOutputterBase, ProxyPlaceOutputter, TabContentProxyPlaceOutputter

    public interface ProxyOutputter
    Interface of classes that are able to output the code of a specific type of proxy. Usually produced via ProxyOutputterFactory.
